    "title": "What is Anchor Link?",
    "slug": "anchor-link",
    "featuredImage": "https://imagedelivery.net/uIVQ6NXJhv6uJPgWapIyVQ/393aa8b2-1526-4033-f3cd-27fac1605200/large",
    "category": "blog",
    "authorName": "Mackey Martin",
